}

### Update Cost Center (Change Sub-Section Only)
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "sub_section": "05",
  "remarks": "Moved to different sub-section"
